WEBVTT

00:02:59.267 --> 00:03:02.861
Keshtu s'ka barriera akustike.

00:03:03.590 --> 00:03:09.415
Kur vendos shume femije 
ne nje kuti qetesie,

00:03:09.415 --> 00:03:12.733
disa prej tyre nervozohen shume.

00:03:12.733 --> 00:03:14.985
Por ne kete kopesht,

00:03:14.985 --> 00:03:18.415
nuk kane arsye te nervozohen.

00:03:18.415 --> 00:03:21.225
Sepse ky kopesht s'ka kufij.

00:03:21.225 --> 00:03:23.422
Drejtori thote

00:03:23.422 --> 00:03:27.425
nese djali qe eshte ne cep
s'do te qendroje ne dhome

00:03:27.425 --> 00:03:29.120
e leme te dale.

00:03:29.120 --> 00:03:32.279
Ai do te kthehet, s'ka nga shkon
eshte rreth.